{"tid":1665050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於遊行散水PoPo搜車既建議","createTime":"2019-10-20T12:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T12:46:13.000Z","uid":39880,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28414bfcc188c6badc64609e06857b81d4411899","tid":1665050,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"其實近呢兩次大遊行（港島及九龍）都見到<br />\nPOPO改左戰術，開始會係<strong>公路搜查巴士</strong><br />\n尤其係<strong>屯元天，沙田大埔區</strong>更加明顯<br />\n每次搜車都會有幾位手足被捕！<br />\n就算無事都被折騰三四個鐘，難受到仆街<br />\n所以我覺得散場之後手足應該要：<br />\n一）避免直接由示威區坐巴士離開<br />\n其實見到班狗最主要都係查由示威區開出既車<br />\n持屯天元做例子；上次專查過海巴，今次專查油尖旺X線<br />\n所以大家散場時不妨考慮先去其他區，再坐車番自已住果頭<br />\n例如今日我坐葵涌開既車就係屯公無事，消息指沙田開既車都安全<br />\n二）留意TG消息，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">並且同其他人分享</span><br />\n我相信好多手足都會有留意TG<br />\n但係唔係每位和理非特別係上左年紀既會有<br />\n所以見到有消息既，不妨係車站提其他人邊度有危險<br />\n用番堅定小小既語氣叫人唔好坐／建議人地點坐<br />\n因為淨係講邊度邊度有狗可能d人會睇少左成件事<br />\n就算上左車都好都提下其他人邊個位有人查車<br />\n覺得自已架車高危既就叫有文具既手足落車<br />\n三）換衫換衫換衫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都十月喇，仲戴口罩著黑衫走搏查咩！！！！！！</span></strong><br />\n戴多件衫換左佢都唔係好煩姐，係咪？<br />\n<br />\n我相信搜車呢樣野黎緊都繼續會有<br />\n而且只會更多公路／地方中招<br />\n即使和理非寶寶身上咩都無 文具都無<br />\n俾人咁搞一搞三四個鐘，屎尿唔俾痾野又唔俾食<br />\n你都唔好話歎阿<br />\n<br />\n另外再講多樣野，車上面d狗係會Mon Po<br />\n佢一路睇住你一路上網睇連登架！唔好好似我咁傻豬自爆！<br />\n（可以起我底睇下我上次奶野經歷）<br />\n（另外多謝番上次果隻防暴見我餓打算請我食朱古力，不過真係不了）<br />\n希望唔好咁快沉底啦 唔想次次都咁多手足奶野番唔到屋企"},{"pid":"d69a7264b1fc33020a2a4e874cb5c126152dc191","tid":1665050,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"自推一次"},{"pid":"9f986753676654bb3c7d46e842da47ce4bf8d8b6","tid":1665050,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bba7778c1e155a6d931079bdda3525028deed349","tid":1665050,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a8a86b779e9664a862da087dc671f2951d3569e","tid":1665050,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"返緊西北 希望無事"},{"pid":"7739bc67000cfd2a6ad7ab4f80bea631cc6c4271","tid":1665050,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"自推兩次"},{"pid":"484079cd3e25177eea96fe233a11ea2b2da12eb8","tid":1665050,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"自推三次"},{"pid":"63dbd6891588766444f3faaa19ef13b5b56dccb5","tid":1665050,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"藍色清真寺單野，請集中火力地推！<br />\n穆斯林美國眾議員Ilhan Omar同Rashida Tlaib、倫敦市長簡世德。媒體方面主力搵阿拉伯半島電視台。<br />\n<br />\n推Po：<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eoDkkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eoDkkT</a><br />\n<br />\n@AJEnglish @IlhanMN @RashidaTlaib @SadiqKhan<br />\n<br />\n水炮車射清真寺片段<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1185837629146718208?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1185837629146718208%3Fs%3D19&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=854f2f58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1185837629146718208%3Fs%3D19&h=ba3f77c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1185837629146718208?s=19</a></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1185833168571469824?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbadiucao%2Fstatus%2F1185833168571469824%3Fs%3D19&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=9d1f459b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbadiucao%2Fstatus%2F1185833168571469824%3Fs%3D19&h=d1d32937\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1185833168571469824?s=19</a></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/jack_100d/status/1185834567917137920?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt